      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON COPY (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.41 beating Compton Franky. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from 10 starts. Great chance to get the job done again. RUSTY WHEELS (1) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (17.63) in a Grade 5 at Healesville latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can hit the frame this time. LEKTRA HANK (7) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (23.54) but scored five back at this track (23.26). Form here at this distance is sound. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. One of the main contenders. ASTON AZUL (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
